            <supports>Alpha Druid Circle</supports>
            <description>
                <p>The Circle of the Prime Elements is made up of wanderers and sages who keeps the connection between the elemental planes and the material plane safe and under control. These druids are often rumored to be destructive and dangerous, which is true, but only when they need to be.</p>
                <div element="ID_SWECKY_RDDT_UA_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_CIRCLE_OF_THE_PRIME_ELEMENTS_ELEMENTAL_ATTUNEMENT" />
                <div element="ID_SWECKY_RDDT_UA_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_CIRCLE_OF_THE_PRIME_ELEMENTS_CIRCLE_SPELLS" />
