            <element name="Elemental Attunement" type="Archetype Feature" source="r/Unearthed Arcana" id="ID_SWECKY_RDDT_UA_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_CIRCLE_OF_THE_PRIME_ELEMENTS_ELEMENTAL_ATTUNEMENT">
                <description>
                    <p>Starting at 2nd level, you have begun your journey to become one with the elements. Choose air, earth, fire, or water. This is the element you are attuned to; gaining you an Elemental Shape and Circle Spells associated with it. During a long rest, you can attune yourself to another of the four elements, but you can only be attuned to one element at a time.</p>
                    <p class="indent">Also, you can speak, read, and write Primordial.</p>
                </description>
                <sheet>
                    <description>Choose air, earth, fire, or water. This is the element you are attuned to. During a long rest, you can attune yourself to another of the four elements, but you can only be attuned to one element at a time.</description>
                </sheet>
