            <element name="Elemental Mastery" type="Archetype Feature" source="r/Unearthed Arcana" id="ID_SWECKY_RDDT_UA_ARCHETYPE_FEATURE_CIRCLE_OF_THE_PRIME_ELEMENTS_ELEMENTAL_MASTERY">
                <description>
                    <p>At 10th level, your mastery over the elements has increased significantly. Your Elemental Shapes lasts for 10 minutes and each form gains the following benefits:</p>
